channel.title: Drunk Party
channel.description:
I was just at a friend's party last night where everybody but me and my brother got completely dunk.
One guy stood on a quad and tried to do a back flip off of it, he made a full flip and then kept going so he landed flat on his back. He also got on a dirt bike and started it up but my other drunk friend tackled him and pulled him away in an arm lock before he could hit the gas. He put on my friend's sister's girly tanktop too. He was walking around drunk acting tough and acting like a wannabe gangster while wearing a really girly tanktop. :smiley:
Another friend drunk dialed a girl I really like because he is going out with her sister and wanted to talk with her. It was midnight so he got the voicemail but he was so drunk he thought it was still ringing. We talked to my friend for about 2 minutes telling him how drunk he was before realising that the entire conversation was being left on the girl's voicemail. I don't know if I should be cracking up or really pissed off.
My brother brought a camera and was filming most of it, he got this of him slapping my drunk friend, but he wasn't filming when the guy did the flip. > :frowning: ![](upload://AkIw5EgJeAw79nJfBVpTaWc08zL.gif)
